<h4>Link Outline Reset</h4>

<p>Williamson recommends adding these link styles for assistive devices/user agents for accessibility and to prevent Chrome from applying non-assigned colors to the <code>outline</code>:</p>

<pre>
a:focus {
     outline: thin dotted;
}
a:hover, a:active {
     outline: 0;
}
</pre>

<p class="note">NOTE: In an <code>a</code> tag, setting <code>text-decoration:</code> to <code>none;</code> will remove the <code>outline</code>.</p>